text.tspan: Directions: Wash face with Yogic Beauty Face
Pack. Dry with soft towel. Massage few drops
onto the face. Allow to absorb. Take a few deep
breaths and bring your attentions to stillness.
Final Ingredients: Grapeseed, Almond, sesame oil, rose hip oil, anantamool, licorice, shatavari, gotu kola, kum kum essential oils of palmarosa, rose, sweet orange, helichrysum, usheera
Final Ingredients: Grapeseed oil, sunflower oil, coconut oil, licorice, neem, amalaki, guduchi, brahmi, bhringraj, essential oils of jasmine, sandalwood, geranium, helichrysum
Final Ingredients: Grapeseed oil, Sunflower oil, safflower oil, licorice, manjistha, lodhra, amalaki, triphala, dashmool, saffron, essential oils of lemon, lavender, helichrysum, mint, orange
**Kumkumadi Oil (brightening): (I want this one to follow a kumkumadi oil recipe)
Grapeseed oil, sesame oil, saffron, licorice, manjistha, papaya, turmeric, nargis essential oil
Tridoshic Face Pack (face cleanser for combo to oily/acneic skin):
Final Ingredients: Moong bean powder, licorice, anantamool, aloe vera, musta, lodhra, manjistha, priyangu, turmeric, kumkum, clay, orange peel
**Tridoshic Oil Cleanser (face cleanser for dry skin):
Grapeseed oil, olive oil, aloe vera, lemon essential oil, sweet orange essential oil
